<h2>Developer Tool and API Directories</h2>
<p>These directories target developers, engineers, and technical decision-makers. High-value for developer tools, APIs, SDKs, and infrastructure products.</p>
<p><strong>68. <a href="https://github.com/topics/awesome">GitHub Awesome Lists</a></strong>. Community-curated lists for every tech category. Getting included in a relevant "awesome" list sends consistent referral traffic. Submit a PR to the list maintainer.</p>
<p><strong>69. <a href="https://devhunt.org/">DevHunt</a></strong>. Product Hunt for developer tools. Built by developers, for developers. Free launch platform with upvoting.</p>
<p><strong>70. <a href="https://devresources.info/">Dev Resources</a></strong>. Collaborative platform for discovering and sharing development resources. Categorized into AI, design, programming, and more.</p>
<p><strong>71. <a href="https://apilist.fun/">API List</a></strong>. Public API directory for developers. If your product has a public API, list it here for developer discovery.</p>
<p><strong>72. <a href="https://rapidapi.com/hub">RapidAPI Hub</a></strong>. The largest API marketplace. Developers search here to find and test APIs. Essential for any API-first product.</p>
<p><strong>73. <a href="https://www.programmableweb.com/">ProgrammableWeb</a></strong>. One of the oldest API directories. Strong domain authority and developer trust despite reduced activity.</p>
<p><strong>74. <a href="https://github.com/agamm/awesome-developer-first">awesome-developer-first</a></strong>. GitHub list of developer-first tools and products. Curated by the community with strict quality standards.</p>
<p><strong>75. <a href="https://devsuite.com/">DevSuite</a></strong>. Platform for discovering and evaluating software development tools. Comparison features help buyers decide.</p>
<p><strong>76. <a href="https://www.everydev.ai/">EveryDev.ai</a></strong>. Developer-curated AI tools directory. Specifically built for developer audiences looking for AI integrations.</p>
<p><strong>77. <a href="https://aifordevelopers.org/">AI for Developers</a></strong>. Curated AI SDKs, copilots, and APIs for developers. Niche directory with high-intent developer traffic.</p>
<p><strong>78. <a href="https://github.com/tokyo-dal/awesome-ai-coding-tools">Awesome AI Coding Tools</a></strong>. GitHub list of AI-powered coding tools. Active community with regular updates.</p>
<p><strong>79. <a href="https://webcurate.co/">WebCurate</a></strong>. Hand-curated selection of 430+ developer tools organized by category. Editorial quality control on submissions.</p>
<p><strong>80. <a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/showhn.html">Hacker News (Show HN)</a></strong>. Not a directory, but "Show HN" posts generate massive developer attention. A front-page Show HN can bring 10,000+ visitors in a day.</p>
