<p><strong>115. <a href="https://www.fosshub.com/">Fosshub</a></strong>. Clean and fast open source software downloads directory. Editorial review process for quality control.</p>
<p><strong>116. <a href="https://ossinsight.io/">OSS Insight</a></strong>. GitHub data-driven insights on open source projects. Not a traditional directory, but gets your project indexed.</p>
