<h3>Submission Tips That Save Time</h3>
<p><strong>Prepare these assets before you start:</strong>
- Company logo (square, 512x512px minimum)
- Product screenshots (3-5 high-quality images)
- 50-word description
- 150-word description
- 500-word description
- Founder headshot and bio
- Pricing page URL
- Demo or signup URL</p>
<p><strong>Track every submission</strong> in a spreadsheet with columns for: directory name, submission date, approval status, listing URL, and backlink type (dofollow or nofollow).</p>
<p><strong>Do not copy-paste the same description everywhere.</strong> Search engines penalize duplicate content. Write 3-4 description variants and rotate them across directories.</p>
